com.steelypip.powerups.io

Class StringPrintWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.Writer
      • java.io.PrintWriter
        • com.steelypip.powerups.io.StringPrintWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, Flushable, Appendable, AutoCloseable

    public class StringPrintWriter
extends PrintWriter
    Implements a reusable print-writer that targets a string. It is reusable in the sense that you can extract the internal string at any time as many times as you like and you can reset it to empty as well.
